node.text: New jacket, who dis? We are thrilled to announce @bcortes297 as our newest Principal Bartender and @nielwuflo as our newest Apprentice. They earned their jackets through hard work and dedication, and we are so proud to have them as part of our EO family. Come have a drink with them this week! #TeamEO #EONY

node.text:
This Tuesday & Wednesday (August 10 & 11), revel in a taste of #Yucatán at the @zapotebar pop-up happening here at EO from 6pm-10pm. Zapote Bar’s team will be taking over EO to serve their signature cocktails & bites along with our full menu. This is one event not to miss!

*Reservations required for dining. Walk-ins are welcome for cocktails and appetizers. #EONY #EOxZapoteBar

node.text: Your summer joyride—the EO Maserati. @tanqueraygin shaken with lemon juice, fresh basil, apple liqueur & chamomile cordial. #EONY #maserati (📸: @joanna.lin)

node.text:
Save the date! We’re bringing #RivieraMaya vibes to NYC with our “EO Meets Zapote” pop-up taking place next Tuesday & Wednesday (August 10th & 11th from 6pm-10pm). Come enjoy signature drinks & bites from @rwmayakoba’s @ZapoteBar along with EO signatures and classics.

*Reservations required for dining. Walk-ins are welcome for cocktails and appetizers. #EONY #EOxZapoteBar

node.text: Giddy up for our “Yankee Notions”. It’s made with EO x @woodfordreserve Master’s Collection Double Oaked Bourbon—a nightcap you won’t regret. #EONY (📸: @joanna.lin)
